# Optional: raises GitHub API rate limit from 60/hr (anonymous) to 5000/hr.
# Needed for reliable CI builds; local dev can omit it and rely on the
# node_modules/.cache TTL to stay within the anonymous quota.
#
# Generate a fine-grained token with "public repositories (read)" scope
# at https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta
GITHUB_TOKEN=
